data.description: Welcome to your new turn-key home! This charming townhome in the Lakes of Summerville offers 2 bedrooms and 2.5 baths. Situated near Summerville Hospital, Trident Hospital, and Charleston Southern University.Upon entering through the front porch, a sense of warmth embraces you. The open great room features a vaulted ceiling and a ceiling fan, creating a welcoming atmosphere. Revel in the beauty of the vinyl plank flooring that extends through the great room and kitchen eat-in areas.  The recently renovated half bath on the first floor adds a touch of modern elegance.This home boasts dual master bedrooms, each equipped with a newly renovated en-suite bathroom and a spacious walk-in closet.The upstairs master bedroom offers a picturesque view of the lake. Additionally, there's a small lft area currently serving as a home office, adding a versatile touch to the space. Enjoy updated light fixtures throughout.  Step outside the dining area onto a patio with a delightful lake view and a newly fenced-in backyard, perfect for outdoor enjoyment.  Buyer/buyer's agent to verify anything deemed important such as school zones, square footage, flood zones, etc.
